OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FCyclists and walkers slowly amassed on
OL,7,Fthe pebble beaches on the eastern
OL,8,Fshore of Coniston Water from the early
OL,9,Fhours.
OL,11,FThe smart brought deck chairs to
OL,12,Fsettle in for the long haul of
OL,13,Fwaiting. The talk was all about the
OL,14,Fbiting cold wind no-one had really
OL,15,Fanticipated and when...? When would
OL,16,Fthey get to see Bluebird K7 back on
OL,17,Fthis water for the first time since
OL,18,Fthat awful day in 1967?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
