FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FSome spectators saw the tragedy unfold
OL,7,Fthat day. One man had tears in his
OL,8,Feyes as he told me of seeing it at the
OL,9,Fage of 6, before he heard it, as the
OL,10,Fsound followed down the lake.
OL,12,FHis superhero, Donald Campbell, had
OL,13,Fsunk to the bottom of the water. Three
OL,14,Fhours later his Dad told him "even
OL,15,Fsuperheroes can't hold their breath
OL,16,Fthat long".
OL,18,FBut Donald Campbell's place in
OL,19,FConiston's history started way before
OL,20,F1967.
OL,26,@vD@^OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FBy then, it was firmly the place: the
OL,7,Fgreats of international water speed
OL,8,Frecords - the gods of that world -
OL,9,Fright here.
OL,11,FA second home. A spiritual home. A
OL,12,Fmeticulous love, care and worship of a
OL,13,Fphenomenal craft.
OL,15,FA young lad in a small Lakeland
OL,16,Fvillage could be part of that world.
OL,17,FAnthony Robinson, or Robbie as he's
OL,18,Fknown locally, told ITV News Border
OL,19,Fabout measuring out 56kg of sand to
OL,20,Fget the weight right on the boat.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FHe said: "For a 22-year-old lad to be
OL,7,Fpart of something like that was out of
OL,8,Fthis world. How lucky I was to meet so
OL,9,Fmany people, who were so dedicated. I
OL,10,Flearned an awful lot from that, about
OL,11,Flife and what you have to do to get
OL,12,Fon. You know, you just didn't give up
OL,13,Fat the first hurdle.
OL,15,FHe was one of the first on the scene
OL,16,Ffollowing the crash.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,F"I was on the lake at the time. She
OL,7,Fjust looked absolutely perfect. The
OL,8,Flast thing that I think anybody
OL,9,Fthought of at that moment was that
OL,10,Fsomething could go wrong in ten
OL,11,Fminutes time. Because she just looked
OL,12,Fwonderful.
OL,14,FHe says it took a long time for the
OL,15,Fpeople of Coniston to accept what had
OL,16,Fhappened.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,F"For quite a long time afterwards, the
OL,7,Fvillage kind of took a while for it to
OL,8,Fcome to terms with what had happened
OL,9,Fbecause we'd been used to so many
OL,10,Fsuccessful record attempts of
OL,11,FConiston. I think, they didn't want to
OL,12,Fmake money out of the tragedy. That
OL,13,Flasted quite a long time, until
OL,14,Finterestingly, somebody said, you
OL,15,Factually need to do something, because
OL,16,Fit helps to keep the memory alive.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,F"Seeing that and hearing the roar of
OL,7,Fthat engine again... Most of them are
OL,8,Fgoing to be good memories because they
OL,9,Fwere. Just one more time to see her up
OL,10,Fon that lake, doing what she did best."
OL,12,FIt's a long history that continues
OL,13,Ftoday. Power Boat Records Week is
OL,14,Fstill held on Coniston Water every
OL,15,Fyear. It is forged into Coniston's
OL,16,Fidentity.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FLocal hospitality businessman and
OL,7,Fmember of the K7 Club, Phil Johnston,
OL,8,Fsaid: "A lot of the people that come
OL,9,Fwith the boats every year, of course
OL,10,Fhave got to know local people and are
OL,11,Ffriends. And so it's a lovely,
OL,12,Ffriendly community.
OL,14,F"The Bluebell Festival this year has
OL,15,Fmeant that the middle of May will not
OL,16,Fbe as quiet a time. There are an awful
OL,17,Flot of local people employed here in
OL,18,Ftourism, and it's all a matter of
OL,19,Fsafeguarding their jobs. And a
OL,20,Fwonderful tribute to that very brave
OL,21,Fman."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FYou could not have written the last 60
OL,7,Fyears. Bluebird K7 was raised by Bill
OL,8,FSmith and the Bluebird Project and
OL,9,Frestored so she could run again. There
OL,10,Fwere a lot of feelings about whether
OL,11,Fthat was right and then once raised,
OL,12,Fwhat to do with her.
OL,14,FEventually she came back to Coniston
OL,15,Fto be housed in the Bluebird wing of
OL,16,Fthe Ruskin Museum, which was built for
OL,17,Fher.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FThe streets were lined with cheers and
OL,7,Ftears as she returned home. There is
OL,8,Feven more emotion as she prepares to
OL,9,Ftake to that water once more. Talking
OL,10,Fto people, no-one really knows how
OL,11,Fthey will feel seeing her.
OL,13,FMany in Coniston have been involved
OL,14,Fbut the Bluebird K7 Festival is
OL,15,Forganised by the Ruskin Museum.
OL,16,FDirector Tracy Hodgson told ITV
OL,17,FBorder: "The locals treat him well
OL,18,Fthey called him the adopted son. So he
OL,19,Fmeant a lot to the locals and I think
OL,20,FConiston to him.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,F"He's buried in their local graveyard.
OL,7,FShe was raised in 2001 by Bill Smith
OL,8,Fand the Bluebird Project. They
OL,9,Frestored her to working condition. She
OL,10,Fwas run on Bute in 2018. But she came
OL,11,Fback in 2024.
OL,13,F"I mean, a lot of people remember the
OL,14,Fcrash. They're of a certain age, but
OL,15,Fwe want to get the message out to the
OL,16,Fyounger generation. We are making
OL,17,Fhistory as we speak: one last run on
OL,18,FConiston will hopefully be talked
OL,19,Fabout for years to come."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FAlmost 70 years from his death, Donald
OL,7,FCampbell is still part of Coniston,
OL,8,Fand always will be.
OL,10,FThat history is still being made. It
OL,11,Fis perhaps fitting that there was so
OL,12,Fmuch waiting around, the time expected
OL,13,Fon the water regularly pushed back.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1778526672
OL,3,CThe wait is over - Bluebird K7
OL,4,Chydroplane runs on Coniston Water
OL,6,FDonald Campbell's team hit many
OL,7,Fproblems before getting Bluebird K7 to
OL,8,Frecord-breaking speeds. Back then, the
OL,9,Fcrowds began trailing off as yet again
OL,10,Fit didn't happen, but they still came.
OL,11,FThe fever to see that moment in
OL,12,Fhistory was there in full swing in
OL,13,F1967.
OL,15,FThis week, despite the wait and the
OL,16,Fcold, they would wait. And history has
OL,17,Fbeen made again, a celebration of
OL,18,FConiston's adopted son.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
